# Mini SIEM System (Python)

A lightweight Security Information and Event Management (SIEM) system built using Python.

## Features
- Log collection via agent (Linux/Windows ready)
- Rule-based threat detection (brute force, suspicious activity)
- SQLite-backed alert storage
- Web dashboard with charts (Chart.js)
- Real-time alert visualization

## Tech Stack
- Python (Flask)
- SQLite
- Chart.js

## Architecture
Agent → Server → Detection Engine → Database → Dashboard

## Setup
1. Install dependencies:
   pip install -r requirements.txt

2. Run server:
   cd server
   python app.py

3. Run dashboard:
   cd dashboard
   python app.py

## Future Improvements
- Docker deployment
- Authentication system
- Advanced correlation rules